  Se3-kan Lang5 Tioh8 ChaiN2-iuN7`KiaN5 Chiah Thang Tit-tioh8 Kiu3. 
  (Thak8 Chhut Ai-kip8 ki3 12:24--30.) 
  Sin Ku7 iok e5 chong2-chi2, chiu7-si7 hou7 se3-kan lang5 oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 kong-lo5, chiah thang bian2 ti7 sim2-phoaN3 e5 si5 teng7 choe7. Siong5-se3 chha5-kho2 Seng3-keng chheng chiuN ban7 chat, hoan2 hok koe2-beng5, bo5 m7 si7 ai3 se3-kan lang5 siong5-se3 beng5 kiu3-un e5 hoat-tou7, sit8-chai7 Seng3-keng sou2 lun7 e5 su7-chek pau-ham5 kek8 khoah. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 tit-tioh8 kiu3 chhut Ai-kip8 e5 khou2-lan7, si7 tai7-seng piau2-beng5 lan2 au7-tai7 e5 lang5 oe7 thoat-li7 choe7-ok tang7-taN3 e5 ki-koan. Sou2-i2 lan2 thak8 chit chiuN, eng-kai khoaN3 choe3 Siong7-te3 kiu3-to7 heng5-chong7 e5 tou5, kap lan2 teh-beh tit kiu3 e5 lang5 u7 toa7 li7-ek. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 ti7 Ai-kip8 be7 thau2-pang3 e5 keng2-hong2 chhin-chhiuN7 iau2-be7 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 choe7-jin5. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 tit-tioh8 thau2-pang3 sou2 eng7 e5 hoat-tou7 chhin-chhiuN7 tai7-seng piau2-beng5 Ia5-sou Ki-tok au7 jit8 kiu3 choe7-jin5 sou2 eng7 e5 hoat-tou7. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 tiam3 Ai-kip8 choe3 kek8 kho2-lin5 e5 lou5-chai5, bo5 lang5 oe7 pang-chan7 in, ia7 bo5 lang5 goan7 pang-chan7 in, in ka-ki7 ki3-jian5 boe7 ka-ki7 pang-chan7, siat-su2 ka-ki7 kiu3, koh-khah kan-khou2, kap be7 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3 e5 choe7-jin5 saN-tang5. Be7 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3 e5 lang5 choe3 cheng5-iok8 e5 lou5-chai5, chhin-chhiuN7 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 choe3 Ai-kip8 e5 lou5-chai5. Be7 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3 e5 lang5 choe3 choe7-ok e5 lou5-chai5, eng2 bo5 thau2-pang3 e5 jit8, chhin-chhiuN7 kha chhiu2 hou7 lang5 pak8--teh, thong sin-khu boe7-oe7 chu7-iu5. Se3-kan lang5 choe3 m7-tioh8, choe3 phaiN2, tauh8-tauh8 hoan7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 gi7 e5 siu7-khi3, ka-ki7 chai boe7 siam2-pi7 chiong-lai5 e5 heng5-hoat8. Kai-chai3 Ia5-sou hian3 ka-ki7 e5 sin-khu, chhin-chhiuN7 kou2-cha2 lang5 lau5 iuN5-a2 e5 huih hian3 choe3 che3-mih8, choe3 ban2-hoe5 choe7-ok e5 le2, sou2-i2 Siong7-te3 chiu7 hoaN-hi2 chiap-lap8 lan2 u7 choe7 e5 lang5. 
  Tng si5 Siong7-te3 kang3 chai-e7 ti7 Ai-kip8 kok, in-ui7 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 khia7-khi2 ti7 hit sou2-chai7, boe7 bian2-tit kap Ai-kip8 lang5 tang5-siu7 chai-lan7. Kai-chai3 Siong7-te3 cha2-cha2 lip8 chit8 e5 hoat-tou7, kiu3 keng2-soan2 e5 peh-siN3 li7-khui, na7 bo5, I2-sek-liat8 lang5 e5 toa7-kiaN2 kap thau5-chui2 e5 cheng-siN, iah8 tioh8 kap Ai-kip8 lang5 e5 toa7-kiaN2 thau5-chui2 cheng-siN piN5-piN5 siu7 phah--si2. (Chhut 12: 19[29].) Lan2 se3-kan lang5 iah8 si7 an2-ni. Seng3-keng kong2, “Sin3 I e5 lang5 boe7 siu7 sim2-phoaN3, m7 sin3 e5 lang5 i2-keng siu7 sim2-phoaN3, in-ui7 m7 sin3 Siong7-te3 tok8-siN kiaN2 e5 mia5.” (Iok-han7 3:18.) Tui3 che khoaN3, lan2 e5 choe7 i2-keng tiaN7-tioh8, chi2-u7 heng5-hoat8 be7 kau3 sin-chiuN7 na7-tiaN7. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 ti7 Ai-kip8, Siong7-te3 e5 kiu3-un be7 hian2-chhut e5 tai7-seng, in e5 choe7 i2-keng tiaN7-tioh8--lah. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 than3 Siong7-te3 e5 hoan-hu3, chiong iuN5-a2 e5 huih lai5 boah siang-peng5 mng5-khia7, thong ke e5 lang5 long2 chu7-chip8 ti7 boah-huih e5 mng5-lai7, m7 hou7 in chhut--khi3. IuN5-a2 eng7 he2 sio-sek8 chiah8 e5 si5 tioh8 ha5-toa3, chheng7-oe5, kiah8 koaiN2-a2 teh chiah8, chit kui2 hang7 e5 hoan-hu3 long2 tioh8 sit8-heng5, te7-it iau3-kin2--e5 chiu7-si7 hiu3-huih. Siong7-te3 kong2, “Goa2 chit8-e7 khoaN3-kiN3 u7 huih, chiu7 poaN5-ke3 lin2 e5 chhu3.” Lan2 chha5-kho2 huih e5 i3-su3 bo5 oh beng5, chiu7-si7 piau2-beng5 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih. IuN5-a2 e5 huih kiu3 I2-sek-liat8 lang5, chiu7-si7 tai7-seng piau2-beng5 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 huih kiu3 se3-kan e5 choe7-jin5. Thai5 bo5 choe7 e5 iuN5-a2 lai5 kiu3 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 e5 toa7-kiaN2, chhin-chhiuN7 Seng3-keng kong2, Siong7-te3 e5 IuN5-ko Ki-tok ui7-tioh8 se3-kan lang5 e5 choe7, lau5-huih si2-sit, gi7--e5 thoe3 put-gi7 si2, hou7 sin3 e5 lang5 eng2 boe7 teng7-choe7. An2-ni Ia5-sou e5 si2 chiu7 thang kiu3 sin3 I e5 lang5 tit-tioh8 eng2-oah8, eng2 boe7 kau3 biat8-bo5. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 eng7 iuN5-a2 huih boah ti7 mng5-bai5 mng5-khia7, thong ke e5 lang5 bih ti7 chhu3-lai7, che chiu7-si7 eng7 huih choe3 siam2-pi7 hoan7-lan7 e5 sou2-chai7, oa2-kho3 huih chiu7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Phah-si2 Ai-kip8 lang5 e5 toa7-kiaN2 e5 thiN-sai3 khoaN3-kiN3 huih chiu7 bo5 jip8--lai5. Tiong-kok u7 sou2-chai7 e5 hong-siok8, tu2-tioh8 un-ek8 a2-si7 beh siam2-pi7 sim2-mih8 chai-hai7, tioh8 thai5 koe, iuN5, cheng-siN, chiong huih boah ti7 mng5-bai5 kap sia7-li2 e5 si3-bin7, lai5 siam2-pi7 un-ek8, an-tiaN7 he2-chai. Soe3-han3 gin2-na2 iah8 u7 eng7 huih sia2 “sip8” ji7 ti7 thau5-hiah lai5 siam2-pi7 kui2-sui7. Chit ho7 hong-siok8 m7 chai tui3 siaN2 si5 khi2, chong2-si7 iah8 thang in2 choe3 Po2-huih siok8-choe7 e5 kan-cheng3. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 eng7 huih kou5 ti7 mng5--nih8, chiu7 tit-tioh8 huih e5 po2-hou7, choe7-jin5 lai5 chhe7 Ia5-sou, sin3-hok8 oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou, chiu7 tit-tioh8 Chu2 lau5-huih kong-lo5 e5 pi3-iu7, hoan7-na7 chiu7-kun7 Ia5-sou, ka-ki7 jin7 choe3 choe7-jin5, beng5 chai sim2-phoaN3 boe7 to5-siam2--tit, siuN7 bih ti7 Ia5-sou e5 huih e7. Siong7-te3 bat kong2, “KhoaN3-kiN3 mng5-bai5 mng5-khia7 boah-huih, tek-khak poaN5-ke3 in e5 mng5.” (Chhut 12:23.) In-ui7 an2-ni in bo5 giau5-gi5, m7-kaN2 pian7-pok, chi2-u7 siong-sin3 Ia5-sou thoe3 in si2, si7 u7 kong-hau7, oe7 kiu3 i bian2-tit Siong7-te3 e5 toa7 siu7-khi3, chiu7 chiau3 Siong7-te3 kiu3 un e5 hoat-tou7 choe3, bo5 m7 tit-tioh8 peng5-an. 
  I2-sek-liat8 lang5 ti7 Ai-kip8 siu2 PoaN5-ke3 choeh, sui-jian5 siu2 Siong7-te3 sou2 hoan-hu3 tak8-hang7 e5 le2-sou3, chong2-si7 te7-it m7-thang bo5--e5, chiu7-si7 boah-huih chit-hang7. Siong7-te3 long2 bo5 kong2 khoaN3-kiN3 lin2 io ha5 toa3, kha chheng7 oe5, chhiu2 kiah8 koaiN2, Goa2 chiu7 poaN5-ke3 bo5 hai7--lin2. Siat-su2 u7 lang5 tak8-hang7 chiau3 sou2 hoan-hu3 khi3 kiaN5, ki5-tiong lang3 boah-huih chit8 hang7 bo5 kiaN5, li2 phah-sng3 chaiN2-iuN7? ThiN-sai3 kiam2 m7 si7 iu5-goan5 beh jip8-khi3 thai5 si2 in e5 toa7 kiaN2--mah? Sou2-i2 bo5 lun7 lang5 chaiN2-iuN7 chun-siu2 PoaN5-ke3 choeh, na7 bo5 eng7 huih boah ti7 mng5--nih8, ki5-u5 e5 le2-sou3 sui u7 oan5-choan5 siu2, iu5-goan5 boe7 bian2-tit toa7 kiaN2 si2. Se3-chiuN7 u7 kiaN5 choe3 toan-hong e5 lang5, goa7-phe5 u7 kau3-iu2 e5 khoan2-sit, tit-tioh8 chhu3-piN o-lo2, sim7-chi3 i2-keng hong7-kau3 nia2 soe2-le2, siong5-siong5 u7 lang5 kio3 i choe3 Ki-tok-tou5, peng5-sou3 ia7 chun-siu2 Kau3-hoe7 tak8-hang7 e5 kui-ku2 le2-gi5, in ka-ki7 phah-sng3 m7 kiaN chiong-lai5 e5 sim2-phoaN3, bo5 phah-sng3 bo5 bih ti7 Ia5-sou po2-huih e5 e7-bin7, long2 bo5 un2-tang3, in-ui7 lang5 kho3 ka-ki7 e5 tek-heng7, chong2 boe7 bian2-tit ka-ki7 phian3 e5 ke3-sit. Seng3-keng kong2, “Siong7-te3 boe7 phian3--tit.” Kau3 sim2-phoaN3 e5 si5 boe7 bian2 teng7-choe7, chi2 u7 tit-tioh8 Ia5-sou po2-huih e5 kiu3-un, chu7-jian5 peng5-an bo5 tai7-chi3. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 thai2 oe7 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 kiu3-un? Long2 m7-si7 kho3 chiah8 iuN5-bah iah8 m7-si7 kho3 u7 kiaN5 tak8-hang7 e5 le2-gi5, sou2 kho3 e5 chi2-u7 ti7 mng5-goa7 e5 huih; na7 chiong huih boah mng5-goa7 chiu7 thang tit-tioh8 kiu3, bo5, sui ti7 ke-lai7 chun-siu2 Siong7-te3 e5 hoan-hu3, iah8 bo5 li7-ek, kiaN-liau2 si2-sit iu5-goan5 kau3 ke-lai7 lang5. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 chai hit mi5 u7 hai7-si2 toa7-kiaN2 e5 thiN-sai3 beh tui3 i e5 mng5-khau2 ke3, thiN-sai3 chi2-u7 jin7 beng5 chit8 hang7 mih8 choe3 ki3-ho7, khoaN3-kiN3 chit hang7 mih8, chiu7 chai tioh8 jip8 lai7 phah-si2 toa7 kiaN2 a2 bian2. Chit hang7 mih8 si7 sim2-mih8? Chiu7-si7 boah ti7 mng5-goa7 mng5-khia7, mng5-bai5 e5 huih. ThiN-sai3 long2 bo5 jip8-lai5 khoaN3 lang5 u7 ha5-io, chheng7-oe5, kiah8 koaiN2-a2--bo5, sou2 chu3-i3--e5, mng5--nih8 e5 huih na7-tiaN7. Siong7-te3 kong2, “Goa2 chit8 e7 khoaN3-kiN3 huih chiu7 poaN5-ke3 li2 e5 chhu3.” Chhi3 siuN7 “Li2” ji7 e5 i3-su3, put-ko3 chi2 ko3-jin5 lai5 kong2, long2 bo5 koan2 pat8-lang5 e5 tai7-chi3, tak8 lang5 ka-ki7 choe3 ka-ki7 siu, sim2-mih8 lang5 siong-sin3 chiu7 hit-e5 tit-tioh8 kiu3, sim2-mih8 lang5 m7 kou5 huih chiu7 hit-e5 siu7 choe7. Kau3 ti7 chiah8 bo5 kaN3 piaN2, khou2-chhai3 kap tit-tioh8 kiu3 long2 bo5 koan-he7, na7 mng5 teng2 bo5 huih, chiah8 bo5 kaN3 piaN2, khou2-chhai3 iu5-goan5 bo5 li7-ek. Ti7 I Ko-lim5-to 5:7, u7 chiong chin-chiaN3 kap seng5-sit8 lai5 koe2-beng5 bo5 kaN3 piaN2 e5 i3-su3, khou2-chhai3 e5 i3-su3, chiu7-si7 in-ui7 hoan7-choe7 lai5 iu-bun7, chit nng7 hang7 kap tit-tioh8 kiu3 bo5 kan-siap8, long2 boe7 hou7 choe7-jin5 u7 si-ho5 ng3-bang7 tit-kiu3. Kho2-sioh se3-kan u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 oa2-kho3 chhin-chhiuN7 chit ho7 e5 tai7-chi3, ng3-bang7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Siong5-siong5 thiaN-kiN3 lang5 kong2, “Goa2 hian7-chai7 chhut-lat8 choe3 ho2-lang5.” “Kho2-sioh goa2 chiong5-cheng5 u7 choe3 chin-choe7 m7-tioh8.” Kong2 chi2 nng7 ku3 oe7 e5 lang5 na7 bo5 chap8 hun sin3 Ia5-sou thoe3 i si2, thoe3 I lau5-huih, i chiu7 boe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3, i na7 bo5 eng7 Ia5-sou sou2 lau5 e5 huih choe3 siam2-pi7 choe7 e5 sou2-chai7, kan-ta koe2-piN3, hoan2-hoe2 lai5 ka-ki7 kiu3, eng2 boe7 tit--tioh8. Chun5-sim tiong-hou7 si7 lang5 e5 pun2-hun7, phou kio5 cho7-lou7, toa7 sia3-si3, chin2-che3 song3-hiong lang5, iah8 si7 choe3 oe7 kau3 e5 lang5 sou2 eng-kai tioh8 choe3, chi2 kui2-hang7 long2 boe7 kiu3 lang5. Than3 ho2 li7 phaiN2, hoan2-hoe2 choe7, koe2 ke3-sit, iah8 be7-bat kiu3 chit8 lang5, chiah-e5 long2 si7 siok8 kiu3-un lai7-bin7 sou2 u7 e5 m7 si7 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 toe7-ki. Se3-kan lang5 toan3-toan3 boe7 liah8 kiaN5 teng2-bin7 hiah-e5 su7 chiu7 oe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3, tok8-tok8 oa2-kho3 po2-huih chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Siong5-siong5 khoaN3-kiN3 se3-kan u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 liah8 jiat8-sim choe3 te7 it iau3-kin2, phah-sng3 u7 jiat8-sim, seng5-sim chiu7 u7 ng3-bang7, ki5-sit8 chhin-chhiuN7 bo5 kaN3 piaN2 chit8-iuN7, boe7-oe7 kiu3 ti7 Ai-kip8 e5 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 thoat-li7 kan-khou2, thang chai chin-sit8 jiat8-sim iah8 boe7 kiu3 choe7-jin5. Lang5 sui-jian5 jiat8-sim, u7 si5 i sou2 jiat8-sim si7 chho3-gou7 e5 jiat8-sim, iu5-goan5 bo5 lou7-eng7, chhin-chhiuN7 Po2-lo5 iau2-be7 sin3 to7-li2 i2-cheng5 hit si5 i sui-jian5 kek8 jiat8-sim, iu5-goan5 boe7 tui3 jiat8-sim kiu3--i, kho2-kian3 kan-ta oa2-kho3 jiat8-sim, sit8-chai7 boe7 hou7 lang5 tit-tioh8 kiu3, chi2-u7 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih chiah oe7 kiu3 lang5. 
  U7 lang5 kong2, “Oa2-kho3 Ki-tok Ia5-sou, koh chin7 lat8 choe3 chheng-khi3 e5 lang5, goa2 thang ng3-bang7 tit-tioh8 kiu3.” Chong2-si7 che m7-si7 Siong7-te3 kiu3 lang5 e5 hoat-tou7, Siong7-te3 be7-bat kong2, “Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 huih e5 si5, lin2 chin-chin u7 chiah8 iuN5-bah, Goa2 chiu7 poaN5--ke3.” Iah8 be7-bat kong2, “Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 huih e5 si5, lin2 chin-chin u7 chiah8 bo5 kaN3 piaN2, Goa2 chiu7 poaN5--ke3.” SiaN2-su7 kong2 an2-ni? In-ui7 Siong7-te3 ai3 lang5 chai chi2-u7 kek8 chun-kui3 eng5-kng, choe7-jin5 put-ko3 eng7 chit-e5 hoat-tou7 chiu7 thang tit-tioh8 kiu3. Tu5 “Ia5-sou e5 huih” i2-goa7, bo5 lun7 eng7 sim2-mih8 hoat-tou7, lan2 eng2 boe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Siong7-te3 ki3-jian5 teng7 li2 e5 choe7 li2 chiu7 tioh8 siu7 heng5-hoat8, na7-si7 Ia5-sou ui7-tioh8 li2 sou2 eng-kai siu7 e5 heng5-hoat8, sou2-i2 si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3. Chiau3 Siong7-te3 sou2 tiaN7 tioh8 e5 hoat-lut8, choe7-jin5 eng-kai chiau3 sou2 hoan7 e5 choe7-ok siu7-khou2, siu7 si2, m7-ku2 Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2 si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2 lau5-huih, sou2 lau5 e5 po2-huih I i2-keng thoe3 li2 lau5 lah. Tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 lang5 ti7 thiN-teng2 gim5-si kong2, “Li2 bat siu7 thai5 lau5-huih, tui3 ban7 chok8-siN3 e5 tiong-kan siok8-hoe5 goan2 lai5 kui Siong7-te3.” (Khe2-si7-liok8 5:9.) Choe7-jin5 chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 tit kau3 thian-kok hiong2-siu7 eng5-hoa5, long2 m7-si7 oa2-kho3 ka-ki7 e5 hoan2-hoe2, koe2-piN3, ho2 sou2-kiaN5, a2-si7 choe3 sim2-mih8 im-chek, choan-choan si7 kho3 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih, tui3 an2-ni thang tit-tioh8 eng5-kng. Seng3-keng kong2, “I bat eng7 iuN5-ko e5 huih soe2 i e5 saN kau3 peh8-peh8, tiam3 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 cho7-ui7 cheng5.” (Khe2-si7-liok8 7:14.15.) Na7 bo5, koat-toan3 boe7-tiam3 Siong7-te3 e5 po2-cho7 cheng5. Phah-si2 Ai-kip8 toa7 kiaN2 e5 thiN-sai3 khoaN3-kiN3 mng5-bai5 mng5-khia7 i2-keng boah-huih chiu7 chai mng5-lai7 e5 choe7-jin5 i2-keng si2--lah. Se3-kan lang5 bo5 lun7 hoan7-choe7 loa7 tang7, si2-bo5 chiu7-si7 i e5 po3-eng3, taN i2-keng si2, kiam2 iau2 u7 siaN2 choe7 thang teng7. Hoan7-na7 siok8 Ia5-sou Ki-tok--e5, chaiN2-iuN7 bian2 teng7 choe7? Chiu7-si7 Ia5-sou i2-keng choe3 tai7-piau2 thoe3 choe7-jin5 si2 e5 pin5-ku3. Li2 siuN7 chit-ho7 kiu3-un si7 li2 ka-ki7 sou2 oe7 seng5-chiu7--e5 mah? Li2 iu5-goan5 siuN7 kho3 pun2-sin kiaN5 ho2-su7 chiu7 thang kau3 Thian-tong5--mah? Li2 iu5-goan5 siuN7 choe3 khian5-seng5 lai5 chiuN7 Thian-tong5 mah? Li2 iu5-goan5 siuN7 m7 kho3 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih, beh eng7 pat8 e5 hoat-tou7 chiuN7 Thian-tong5--mah? Kiam2-chhai2 li2 i2-keng seng5-jin7 chi2-u7 Ia5-sou e5 huih oe7 hou7 li2 tit-tioh8 kiu3, li2 kiu3-keng3 choe3 sim2-mih8 lai5 kiu3 ka-ki7? Li2 tau3-ti2 eng7 sim2-mih8 hoat-tou7 lai5 kiu3 ka-ki7? ChhiaN2 li2 soe3-ji7 siuN7, chiah-e5 bun7-toe5 long2 si7 chin iau3-kin2, li2 eng-kai than3-cha2 tiaN7-tioh8. Se3-kan iah8 u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 sim-lai7 put-chi2 moa2-i3 kong2, “Goa2 seng5-jin7 chi2-u7 Ia5-sou oe7 kiu3 lan2.” “Lan2 chai lan2 long2 si7 choe7-jin5.” “Lan2 sin3 Ia5-sou u7 si2.” Chong2-si7 an2-ni chiu7 kau3-giah8--lah-mah? An2-ni chiu7 oe7 tit kiu3--mah? I2-sek-liat8 lang5 poaN3-mi5 e5 si5, na7 kan-ta siuN7 iuN5-a2 i2-keng thai5-lah.” Kiam2 an2-ni chiu7 oe7 kiu3 I2-sek-liat8 lang5--mah? Chiau3 an2-ni chiu7 oe7 kiu3 choe7-ok chap8-hun tang7 e5 choe7 jin5--mah? Sit8-chai7 bo5 kau3-giah8 thang kiu3--in. 
  Siong7-te3 be7-bat kong2, “IuN5-a2 thai5--lah, lin2 chiu7 tit-tioh8 peng5-an.” Siong7-te3 kong2, “Lin2 tioh8 eng7 huih boah ti7 mng5-bai5, mng5-khia7, lin2 bih ti7 lai7-bin7 chiu7 tit-tioh8 peng5-an.” 
  Lin2 boh8-tit ka-ki7 jia-moa5 lai5 an li2 e5 liong5-sim, chhin-chhiuN7 i-seng tah siau-tok8 ioh8 ti7 piN7 e5 phe5-hu, boe7 tu5 hit-e5 piN7-kun, kong2, “Goa2 sin3 Ki-tok u7 si2.” Mou5-kui2 iah8 si7 an2-ni sin3. Li2 phah-sng3 Mou5-kui2 u7 giau5-gi5 Ia5-sou bo5 si2--mah? Mou5-kui2 sit8-chai7 bo5 giau5-gi5, m7-ku2 Mou5-kui2 boe7 oa2-kho3 huih lai5 bih ti7 po2-huih e5 e7-bin7. Li2 chhiat-chhiat m7-thang ka-ki7 su-sim moa2-chiok, pang3 khun3-khun3 kong2, “Goa2 chin peng5-an.” Tek-khak tioh8 chin-sim hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3 choe3 oaN7 sin e5 lang5, chiah thang bih ti7 Ia5-sou e5 lai7-bin7, po2-huih oe7 jia-kham3 li2 chiong5-cheng5 long2-chong2 e5 choe7-siok8, an2-ni it-teng7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. 
  Li2 siuN7 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih u7 siaN2 lou7-eng7? Li2 tau3-ti2 liah8 hit-e5 po2-huih choe3 sim2-mih8 lou7-eng7? Li2 siaN2-su7 iau2 ian5-chhian5 m7 goan7 lai5 kho3 po2-huih choe3 siam2-pi7 chai-hai7 e5 sou2-chai7? Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 beh kong2, “Ah! Li2 kong2--e5 chin tioh8, tak8-hang7 si7 sit8-cheng5 e5 oe7, goan2 long2 bo5 giau5-gi5, iah8 sin3 Seng3-keng, chap8 hun chai tit-kiu3 e5 lou7, chi2-u7 tui3 Ki-tok chit tiau5 na7-tiaN7.” Chit chiong2 lang5 chhui3 sui si7 kong2 kau3 chiah ho2-thiaN, ki5-sit8 sim-lai7 iau2-be7 kho3 Kiu3 Chu2, sou2 kong2--e5 choan5-jian5 bo5 lou7-eng7. Pi2-pheng7 tng si5 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 ti7 Ai-kip8, u7 lang5 ka7 in kong2, koaN2-kin2 boah-huih ti7 mng5-bai5, mng5-khia7 in-ui7 kin-mi5 poaN3-mi5 e5 si5, teh beh lai5 sim2-phoaN3, I2-sek-liat8 lang5 kiam2-chhai2 in3 kong2, “U7 iaN2, ho2, ho2, ian5-chhian5--kui2-jit8-a2 chiah choe3.” Na7 an2-ni, in e5 toa7 kiaN2 chun2-chun2 hou7 thiN-sai3 phah--si2. 
  Hit mi5 chiu7-si7 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 tit-tioh8 oah8-mia7, tit-tioh8 chu7-iu5 e5 khi2-thau5, chit mi5 i2-cheng5 in choe3 lou5-chai5, sui-bong2 oah8, chhin-chhiuN7 si2. Siong7-te3 kong2, “Lin2 tioh8 eng7 chit geh8 choe3 chiaN-geh8.” SiaN2-su7 an2-ni? In-ui7 hit mi5 in u7 bih ti7 huih e5 e7-bin7 chiah u7 siN3-mia7, chiu7-si7 in u7 siN3-mia7 e5 thau5 chit8 jit8, iah8 si7 chiaN5 kok e5 thau5 chit8 jit8. 
  Li2 e5 oah8-mia7 kiu3-keng3 tui3 sim2-mih8 si5 khi2? Chiu7-si7 tui3 oa2-kho3 Ki-tok e5 po2-huih hit si5 khi2, iah8 si7 li2 oah8-mia7 e5 thau5 chit8 jit8. Na7 bo5 kho3 Ki-tok e5 po2-huih, li2 chiu7 bo5 oah8-mia7. He si7 chaiN2-iuN7 kong2? In-ui7 lang5 ham7-loh8 choe7-giat8, chhin-chhiuN7 loh8 ti7 he2-khiN, kap si2 chit8-iuN7. 
  An2-ni li2 eng-kai chaiN2-iuN7 kiaN5 chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3? Tioh8 koaN2-kin2 bih ti7 Ia5-sou e5 e7-bin7, in-ui7 I u7 thoe3 li2 pe5 choe7-giat8 e5 ke3-chiN5, chit-e5 ke3-chiN5 m7-si7 kim, gun5, he3-mih8, po2-poe3, chiu7-si7 eng7 I e5 po2-huih kiu3-siok8 li2 e5 choe7, choe3 li2 siam2-pi7 hoan7-lan7 e5 sou2-chai7. TaN tioh8 koaN2-kin2 oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih kiu3-siok8 li2 e5 choe7-giat8. Siong7-te3 u7 eng3-un2 kong2, “Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 lin2 mng5-khau2 u7 boah-huih chiu7 lang3--ke3-khi3.” Kin-a2 jit8 chiu7-si7 li2 u7 oah8-mia7 e5 jit8, iah8 si7 li2 teng5-thau5 siN e5 jit8. 
  OaN7 IaN5. 
  Goan2 e5 chong-chok8 peng5-sou3 tui3-tiong7 bu2-iong2, ui7 kok tam-tng kan-khou2 si2--e5 chin choe7. Goan2 chou2 ti7 Tiong-kok To7-kong ni5 kan, in-ui7 Tiong-eng sit ho5 khai-chian3, jip8 iaN5-ngou2 choe3 peng. Goan2 peh in-ui7 Eng Go5 nng7 kok chian3-su7, iah8 jip8 kau-chian3 hau7-lo5. Goan2 chek in-ui7 In3-tou7 chok-loan7 iah8 khi3 chhut cheng. Sou2-i2 goan2 chit chok8 siau3-lian5 long2 iong2-kam2, kau3 goa2 chiu7 khah bo5. 
  Goa2 tai7-seng tng hiong-thoan5, put-ko3 chin7 hiuN-li2 tam7-poh8-a2 pun2-hun7 na7-tiaN7, bo5 ku2 u7 i3-su3 jip8 kun-kai3, au7--lai5 khi3 po3 mia5, keng-ke3 i-seng chha5-giam7 sin-the2, chiu7 sang3 goa2 kau3 iaN5-pou7, tak8-jit8 chiau3 si5 chhau-lian7 na2 choe3 khou2-kang. Bo5 tai7-chi3 e5 si5 chio nng7 saN e5 peng5-iu2, jip8 chiu2-koan2 chiah8 chiu2, kong2 chhio3 hi3-hiauh, chiu2 na2 lim, heng3 na2 khi2, tak8 jit8 kou3 thit-tho5. Bo5 kui2 geh8 jit8, kun-leng7 kau3, beh tiau3 goan2 khi3 siu2 pat8-ui7, goan2 chin hoaN-hi2, in-ui7 thang oaN7 sin ho7 saN. IaN5--nih8 pang3 kui2-na7 jit8 hou7 lang5 to3-khi3 pi7-pan7 heng5-li2 kap ke-lai7 saN-si5, kau3 beh khi2-sin cheng5 chit8 mi5, goan2 in-ui7 beh li7-khui pun2 hiuN, sou2-i2 jip8 chhai3-koan2 toa7 lim, chiah8 chui3-chui3 chiah to3--lai5, kau3 iaN5--nih8 the ti7 he2-lou5 piN e5 i2, bo5 soe3-ji7 poah8-loh8 he2-lou5, kai-chai3 tang5-phoaN7 chhah goa2 khi3 bin5-chhng5, na7 bo5 tek-khak sio kau3 chhau3-ta. Goa2 na7 chit mi5 si2-khi3, tek-khak loh8 te7-gek8; ke3-jit8 goa2 peng3 bo5 kong2 cha7-jit8 chiu2-chui3 hiam2 si2, au7--lai5 tioh8 keng2-kai3 goa2 e5 tang5-phoaN7 iah8 bo5 kong2 goa2 chui3 kau3 hiam2-hiam2 hou7 he2 sio--si2. 
  Goan2 tng-peng lang5 u7 phaiN2 hong-siok8, khun3 thiN kng chiu7 lim, tok8-tok8 chiu2-tiam3 be7 khui, sou2-i2 chit cha2-khi2 bo5 lim, kau3 chiah8 jit8-tau3 thiaN-kiN3 pe2-chong2 hia u7 ho2 chiu2, chiu7 khi3 chhe7 i toa7 lim, ti3-kau3 thau5 hin5 bak8 am3, cheng2 tui7 khi3 he2-chhia tiam3, khoaN3-kiN3 kiaN5-lou7 lang5 chiu7 toa7 siaN kap in kong2, “Chai3-hoe7, chai3-hoe7,” ia7 chhiuN3 kui2-tiau5-a2 phaiN2 koa-khek. Ti7 he2-chhia lai7 khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 pan5 “Ui-su-ki3” chiu2, chhui3-khi2 noa7 tit8-tit8 lau5, tiaN7-tioh8 kau3 chhia-cham7 tek-khak boe2 lai5 lim. Bo5 loa7-ku2 kau3 chhia-cham7, chhia chi2-u7 beh theng5 kui2 hun cheng, goa2 kap tang5-phoaN7 saN-kap kau3 koan2-tai3 e5 bin7-cheng5, kiah8-chhiu2 kiaN5-le2, kong2, “ChhiaN2 koaN-tiuN2 chun2 goan2 loh8 chhia boe2 chit8 hang7 chin iau3-kin2 e5 mih8.” Koan2-tai3 bo5 siaN2 beh un2, goan2 ka7 i kong2 si7 kek8 iau3-kin2, lou7-be2 chiah hou7 goan2 khi3. Boe2 kui2-na7 kan chiu7 chhia-lai7 lim liau2-liau2, au7--lai5 kau3 Kho-chhiaN2-su-tek, goan2 koh toa7 lim, tak8-pai2 tioh8 lim kau3 chui3-chui3. An2-ni chu7-iu5 e5 sin-khu, soa3 hou7 chiu2 khu-sok, bo5 lim boe7 ke3-jit8. 
  Kau3 Lun5-tun, goan2 be7 hioh kheh-tiam3, tai7-seng chhe7 chit8 keng chhut-mia5 e5 chiu2-tiam3 lim, bo5 gi5 sou2 kio3-choe3 chhut-mia5--e5, chiu7-si7 u3-oe3 ok-chhok e5 tai7-chi3 teh chhut-mia5, jip8 tiam3 teh lim--e5, long2 si7 bo5 he7-loh8 e5 lang5, in e5 sim-i3 to m7-si7 chiah8 chiu2. PhaiN2 hu7-jin5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 goan2 si7 sin-kheh, khoan2-thai7 choe3 siong7-teng2 lang5, goan2 bo5 beh chhap-teng7--in, tok8-tok8 lim-chiu2 na7-tiaN7, lim-soah koh kau3 pat8 keng tiam3, pi2 tai7-seng--e5 koh khah su, goa2 ho7 in choe3 “Oah8 te7-gek8”, chin-chiaN3 bo5-ok put-chok, goa2 chhin-bak8 khoaN3-kiN3 in ku-ku koai3-koai3 e5 phaiN2-tai7, boe7-hiau2 eng7 oe7 lai5 kong2, tok8-tok8 in3 ti7 thau5-nau2 lai7, bo5 boe7 ki3-tit hit ho7 ok-chhok e5 khoan2, goa2 chiah pi-chian7 to7 iam3-ouN3, ho5-hong3 iaN5-ke3 goa2 e5 lang5? Siong7-te3 kek8 toa7 lin5-bin2 khoan2-thai7--goa2, chiong goa2 ti7 te7-gek8 lai7 kiu3 chhut, hou7 goa2 tui7-loh8 hit tiong-kan, goa2 sou2 kiaN5 bo5 chiau3 hoat-tou7 i2-keng choe7 ni5, kai-chai3 Mou5-kui2 e5 lat8 na2 khah soe-bi5, bo5 ku2 goa2 chiu7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Tang5-phoaN7 tak8 jit8 ti7 kek8 phaiN2 e5 sou2-chai7 lim-chiu2 thiong3-lok8, chiN5-gun5 khai liau2, to3-tng2 siuN7 cheng5-jit8 e5 su7, sit8-chai7 bo5 bi7, koat-tiaN7 koh kui2-na7 jit8 beh koh toa7 lim. 
  Peng5 jit8 i2-keng koan3-si3, na7 chit8 jit8 bo5 chhut-mng5, chiu7 chin bo5 ge7, sou2-i2 saN-kap gi7-lun7 kin-a2-jit8 beh khi3 chui2-siu2 hoe7-tng5 siau-liang5, khiok chai bo5 siaN2 heng3-bi7, iah8 bo5 chiu2 thang lim, m7-ku2 bo5 poaN3-iN5, bo5 te5 thang lim na7 bo5 khi3 koh-khah bo5 i3-su3, sou2-i2 tiaN7-tioh8 beh khi3 hia thit-tho5. Kau3-te3, chiu7 u7 lang5 chih-chiap jip8-khi3, eng7 ho2 te5 saN chhiaN2, bi7 put-chi2 phang. Lim soah, siuN7 beh to3-khi3 iaN5--nih8, hut-jian5 u7 lang5 lai5 kong2, “Lin2 chhiaN2 theng5 tiap8-a2 ku2, u7 bou2 e5 sian-siN beh lai5 kong2 to7-li2, chhiaN2 tai7-ke toa3 teh thiaN.” Goan2 thiaN chit ho7 oe7 bo5 siaN2 i3-ai3, chong2-si7 in-ui7 lang5 hiah ho2 chio-hou, put-pian7 bo5 le2 si5--i, put-ko3 bong2 tiam3 tiap8-a2-ku2. Bo5 phah-sng3 to7-li2 kong2 liau2, koh tioh8 tak8 lang5 chhiam-mia5, khng3 goan2 jip8 kai3-chiu2 hoe7, koat-i3 tui3 kin-a2-jit8 choe3 ho2, bo5 koh lim, kiat Seng3 Sin5 e5 ke2-chi2. Goan2 sim-lai7 m7-ai3 chhiam-mia5, au7--lai5 hou7 peng5-iu2 chhut-lat8 khou2-khng3, chiah than3 in e5 i3-su3 bo5 the, chong2-si7 chhiam-mia5 e5 si5, goa2 tui3 peng5-iu2 phin2 kong2, kin-a2-jit8 chhiam-mia5, bin5-a2-jit8 bo5 sng3-siau3, goan2 long2 bo5 siuN7 tioh8, “Lang5 u7 chheng-ban7 sng3, m7-tat8 thiN chit8 uih,” chiu7-si7 m7-chai i2-keng hou7 Siong7-te3 e5 Sin5 kam2-tong7, hou7 goa2 thoat-li7 hai7 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5 e5 toa7 choe7. Goa2 sui-bong2 siong5-siong5 kau3 chui2-siu2 hoe7-tng5 kap peng5-iu2 tho2-lun7 chin-to7, na7-si7 an2-ni iu5-goan5 boe7 kiu3 goa2, in-ui7 goa2 be7 u7 the5-khi2 Ia5-sou e5 mia5, goa2 iau2 m7-bat Ia5-sou, bo5 tit-tioh8 Ia5-sou, goa2 sim long2 bo5 moa2-i3. Choe3 peng e5 seng3 khah choe7 ngi7, te7-it m7-ai3 ke2-ho2. Bou2 e7-hng goa2 kap chit8 e5 Thian-chu2 kau3 e5 lang5 pian7-lun7 to7-li2, hut-jian5 hou7 i siu7-khi3 hau2-hoah, goa2 iah8 bo5 kap i ke3-kau3, iu5-goan5 kap i pian7-lun7 kau3-lai7 e5 chin-li2, i toa7 siu7-khi3, eng7 kun5-thau5-bu2 cheng goa2 e5 bak8-chiu. Ke3-jit8 koan2-tai3 mng7 bak8-chiu chaiN2-iuN7 tioh8-siong? Goa2 in3 “poah8-to2.” Koan2-tai3 beng5 chai goa2 bo5 lau2-sit8, khiok ia7 bo5 siong5-se3 chha5-mng7. An2-ni goa2 sin3 chong-kau3 iu5-goan5 bo5 lou7-eng7, goa2 iau2-ku2 teh hoan7-choe7. Goa2 be7 tit-tioh8 Ia5-sou, sim-lai7 long2 bo5 moa2-i3, ia7 bo5 u7 sim-lai7 chin-sit8 e5 peng5-an. 
  Kun-iaN5 e5 sin-piN u7 chit8 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5 lang5, khia7-khi2 kui2-na7 keng chhu3-a2, lai7-bin7 siat le2-pai3-tng5 kap cha-keng sou2, iaN5--nih8 e5 peng iah8 put-si5 khi3. Chiong-kun7 Seng3-tan3, lai7-bin7 tioh8 chng tioh8 kat, lau7-m2 kio3 goa2 khi3 tau3 pang-chan7. Goa2 khi3 choe3 kui2-na7-jit8, sim put-chi2 hoaN-hi2, an2-ni goa2 ke3 chit8 e5 Seng3-tan3 long2 bo5 lim chiu2. 
  Peng5-si5 iaN5--nih8 ti7 Seng3-tan3 choeh si7 te7-it khoai3-lok8 e5 jit8, iah8 si7 te7-it kiaN-hiaN5 e5 jit8, chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 bo5 keng3-ui3 Siong7-te3 siong7-chhiaN2 chai thang kiaN, in-ui7 kun-iaN5 tok8-tok8 u7 hoan7-choe7 e5 khoai3-lok8, bo5 chin e5 khoai3-lok8. Ke3 Seng3-tan3 liau2-au7, u7 chit8 e7-hng le2-pai3 soah, lang5 mng7 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5 chaiN2-iuN7? Eng7 siaN2 hoat-tou7 chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3? Koh ka7 goa2 kong2, kiaN5 ho2 chin2-che3--lang5, long2 boe7 hou7 lang5 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Ia5-sou u7 thoe3 lan2 si2, thoe3 lan2 pang3-sak siN3-mia7, tam-tng lan2 e5 choe7-ok. An2-ni kong2, chha-put-to chit8 tiam2 cheng ku2. Kong2 soah, goan2 chiu7 kui7-loh8 saN-kap ki5-to2. Chit mi5 to3-lai5 kun-iaN5, goa2 sim-lai7 kek8 iu-bun7, in-ui7 ai3 ke thiaN tit-kiu3 e5 hoat-tou7, chong2-si7 in-ui7 kun-hoat put-chi2 giam5, tek-khak tioh8 chiau3 si5 to3--lai5. Goa2 tu2-tu2 kiaN5 kau3 nng7-peng5 ui5-chhiuN5 e5 tiong-kan, Siong7-te3 e5 Seng3 Sin5 u7 kek8 toa7 leng5-lek8 kam2-tong7--goa2, hian2-beng5 Ia5-sou thoe3 goa2 sou2 choe3 e5 kong-lo5, goa2 chiu7 chai cha2 goa2 sou2 hoan7 e5 choe7-ok, long2 kap Ia5-sou tang5 teng3 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2, sou2-i2 thang chai, Siong7-te3 in-ui7 Ia5-sou chiong lan2 sou2 u7 e5 choe7-ok oan5-choan5 sia3-bian2. Chit ho7 su-siong2 in3 tiau5 goa2 e5 thau5-nau2, hou7 goa2 chap8 hun khoai3-lok8, chin7-lat8 o-lo2 Ia5-sou, koh kiaN5--kui2-pou7, i2-keng kau3 iaN5 mng5, chiu7 kau mng5-phio3 jip8 iaN5, kau3 khun3-pang5, chit si5 goa2 siuN7 beh jin7 Ia5-sou, teng i2-keng bo5 kng, chong2-si7 he2-lou5 iau2 teh toh8, goa2 chiu7 kui7 ti7 lou5-piN ki5-to2, be7 khun3 e5 tang5-phoaN7 long2 u7 khoaN3--kiN3. Goa2 e5 ki5-to2 bo5 loa7 tng5, in-ui7 goa2 i2-keng thoe3 Ia5-sou choe3 kan-cheng3. Au7--lai5 tek-khak choe3 Ia5-sou e5 hak8-seng, cha2-jit8 sou2 choe3 tak8-hang7 long2 bian2 kong2, tok8-tok8 goa2 sin3 Ia5-sou chiu7 thang tit-tioh8 kiu3. Ke3-jit8, goa2 bin2 saN e5 si5, hut-jian5 thiaN-kiN3 pang5-lai7 nng7 lang5 teh khau-se2 goa2, chit8 e5 liam5-piN toa7 siaN kio3 goa2 kong2, “TiuN Khian, chit ui7 bo5 ke2-ho2 e5 lang5, na7 ai3 choe3 Ia5-sou e5 hak8-seng, tioh8 sit8-heng5 m7-thang ke2- iaN2 choe3.” Goa2 in3 kong2, “Kiu5 Siong7-te3 chan7--goa2, goa2 beh sit8-heng5. Kai-chai3 Siong7-te3 chan7--goa2, goa2 chiah oe7 sit8-heng5.” Goa2 ti7 pang5-lai7 siong5-siong5 thak8 Seng3-keng, sim-lai7 put-chi2 khoai3-lok8. Seng3-keng e5 oe7 chi2-si7 goa2 choe3 lang5 e5 to7-li2. Goa2 goan7 chit8-si3-lang5 eng7 Seng3-keng choe3 chi2-lam5 chiam, bo5 lun7 siaN2-su7 long2 boe7 poaN5-ke3 kui-ku2. 
  Goa2 sin3-kho3 Ia5-sou tit-tioh8 kiu3 liau2-au7, ti7 iaN5--nih8 tng chit bo5 loa7-ku2, sui si7 bo5 ku2, kau3-giah8 oe7 hou7 koaN-tiuN2 peng-su7 chai goa2 cha2-jit8 siaN2-khoan2, soa3 hou7 in chai tui3 taN beh kun-sui5 chi7-chui7. In-ui7 ti7 ou-am3--nih8 e5 kng, tiaN7-tiaN7 chai sio2 ke3-sit, iaN5--nih8 si7 te7-it ou-am3 e5 sou2-chai7, bo5 Siong7-te3 e5 to7-li2 boe7-oe7 u7 kng, chong2 tioh8 u7 Ia5-sou e5 to7-li2 ti7 hit lai7-bin7, chiah oe7 u7 kng. Goa2 beh li7-khui e5 jit8, tui3 chheh-ke3 nih8 theh8 goa2 e5 Seng3-chheh. Chhian-chong2 kong2, “Che si7 hou7 li2 li7-khui chia e5 mih8. Iah8 hou7 li2 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 mih8. Koh, si7 hou7 li2 pang3-sak phaiN2, choe3 ho2 e5 mih8.” 
